'''林肯站'''（{{lang-en|Lincoln Station}}）是[[加拿大|加拿大]][[卑詩省|卑詩省]][[大溫哥華地區|大溫哥華地區]][[高貴林|高貴林]]一座[[溫哥華架空列車|架空列車]][[千禧線|千禧線]]車站。此站位於高貴林市林肯路與松樹路（{{lang|en|Pinetree Way}}）的交界處，鄰近高貴林中心商場，為[[運輸聯線|運輸聯線]]收費架構中三號收費區的其中一個車站。

==歷史==
當局本來沒有打算與[[長青延線|長青延線]]其他車站同期興建林肯站，而只計劃在林肯路夾松樹路之處預留位置待日後興建該站<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.evergreenline.gov.bc.ca/documents/station_design_consultation/EvergreenLineStationArea%20DesignDiscussionGuide.pdf|title=Evergreen Line - Station Area Design Consultation Discussion Guide|page=26|date=2010|publisher=British Columbia Ministry of Transportation|accessdate=2013-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120824065357/http://www.evergreenline.gov.bc.ca/documents/station_design_consultation/EvergreenLineStationArea%20DesignDiscussionGuide.pdf|archive-date=2012-08-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。然而，到了2012年7月19日，加拿大聯邦政府與高貴林市政府宣佈與高貴林中心商場的東主達成協議，三方以公私合夥模式興建林肯站，令該站得以與長青線其他車站一併啓用。車站工程耗資約2800萬元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.partnershipsbc.ca/files-4/documents/Evergreen-Final-Project-Report_2012-03-27.pdf|title=Project Report: Evergreen Line Rapid Transit Project|page=6|date=2013-03|publisher=Partnerships British Columbia|accessdate=2013-06-14}}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，當中聯邦政府的撥款約為700萬元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vancouversun.com/Coquitlam+announces+plans+Lincoln+station+Evergreen+Line/6959452/story.html|title=Coquitlam announces plans for a Lincoln Avenue station on Evergreen Line|publisher=The Vancouver Sun|author=Kelly Sinoski|date=2012-07-19|accessdate=2012-07-20|archive-date=2019-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812094249/http://www.vancouversun.com/Coquitlam+announces+plans+Lincoln+station+Evergreen+Line/6959452/story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2012-07-20/province1342780041d3986205.html|title=高貴林市增闢長青線林肯站|publisher=溫哥華《星島日報》|date=2012-07-20|accessdate=2013-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319003816/http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2012-07-20/province1342780041d3986205.html|archive-date=2016-03-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

此站的前期工程於2013年夏季展開，車站主體建築和高架路軌工程則於同年秋季動工<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.evergreenline.gov.bc.ca/documents/CommunityUpdates/130327_CommunityUpdate5.pdf|title=Community Update No. 5 - Looking ahead: Evergreen Line construction activities|date=2013-06|publisher=British Columbia Ministry of Transportation|accessdate=2013-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605160313/http://www.evergreenline.gov.bc.ca/documents/CommunityUpdates/130327_CommunityUpdate5.pdf|archive-date=2013-06-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，並於2016年12月2日聯同千禧線的長青延線一起開幕<ref name="open-date">{{cite news|last1=Brown|first1=Scott|title=TransLink will open Evergreen Line on Dec. 2|date=2016-11-07|accessdate=2016-11-07|work=Vancouver Sun|url=http://vancouversun.com/news/local-news/translink-will-open-evergreen-line-on-dec-2|archive-date=2016-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107222150/http://vancouversun.com/news/local-news/translink-will-open-evergreen-line-on-dec-2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://bc.ctvnews.ca/tri-cities-rejoice-the-long-awaited-evergreen-line-opens-1.3186748|title=Tri-Cities rejoice: The long-awaited Evergreen Line opens|publisher=CTV Vancouver|date=2016-12-02|accessdate=2016-12-02|archive-date=2016-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203153512/http://bc.ctvnews.ca/tri-cities-rejoice-the-long-awaited-evergreen-line-opens-1.3186748|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

